name: Blinded
description: Blinded by triffid spit! Significant penalties to movement, attack and defence.

name: Cursed
description: Cursed! -2 to all stats and saving throws and -20% to damage resistance for 5 turns.

name: Defensive Stance
description: Defensive Stance provides +2 Strength, +4 Constitution, +2 Saving Throws, and +4 Armor Class for 3 turns, but the Dwarven Defender becomes rooted to the spot for the duration.

name: Cause Disease
description: You have been infected by a disease, and have reduced stats.

name: Generic Remove Effect
description: this effect doesn't do anything. The actual Spell that uses this blank effect will be assigning which effects it will remove from the target. This blank effect is here because al spells must reference an effect tag that they use.

name: Greater Elemental Resistance
description: 70% resistance to heat and cold damage.

name: Hasted
description: The character is hasted, gaining one attack and two additional movement squares for five rounds.

name: Insect Swarms
description: A swarm of biting insects! In addition to immediate damage, this causes penalties to attack and defence for 4 rounds.

name: Minor Curse
description: Minor curse! Reduces attack by 1 and standard damage by 20%.

name: Protection
description: +2 to attack rolls and all saving throws for 10 rounds.

name: Slowed
description: Character is slowed, losing one attack and 2 movement squares per round for five rounds.

name: Sweep Attack
description: Attacks up to three adjacent enemies in one giant sweep of your weapon

name: Longstrider
description: The character gains two additional movement squares for five rounds.
